                <h3 class="legal-heading">Usage of Microsoft Teams and Microsoft 365 Applications</h3>
                <p>The general legal notes provided here also apply to the usage of Microsoft Teams and Microsoft 365 applications.</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>